int SrtmZipFile::getData ( QString  filename,
qint16 **  buffer 
) [static]

Creates a buffer of all the data in the SRTM file.

The uncompressed version is used if available.

Returns:
The length of the side of the data (e.g. 1201 or 3601)
Note:
The buffer returned is owned by the caller of this function and _must_ be freed after usage.
